quran[5]{c,v,t,f}:
  2,1,"Alif-Lâm-Mîm. ",footnotes:1:Asi harufusi ni chimpepe mu isimosimo ya Qur’an. Ni pangali jwine jwaakumanyilila mate gakwe ikaŵeje Allah pe basi.
  2,2,"Achi ni Chitabu changali kaikasya nkati mwakwe, chongolo cha ŵakun'jogopa (Allah)."
  2,3,"Aŵala ŵakasakulupililaga yangaiona, ni akwimikaga Swala mwakolosya, soni mu ichindu yatwapele akasatolaga."
  2,4,"Ni aŵala ŵakasakulupililaga yayatulusyidwe kukwenu, ni yayatulusyidwe paujo penu (mmwe nkanim’biche), ni ya Akhera jamanjao akasakulupilila kusyesyene."
  2,5,"Ŵele ŵanganyao ali pachongoko chakuumila kwa M’mbuje gwao, soni ŵanyao niŵali ŵakupunda."